description:
Popular social media personality, Thyle Knox, has always dreamed of going to New Zealand. He puts a plea out to his loyal followers to help him fund his dream vacation in hopes he’ll eventually raise enough to make his dream a reality.

Upon arriving home one day, Thyle receives an anonymous letter at his front door… inside the letter is a challenge. If he chooses to accept the challenge and successfully complete the task, his anonymous fan promises an immediate financial contribution towards his goal.

What lengths is Thyle willing to go to make this all happen?
title: Fuckerbate - Part 1 RAW
